    {
      "instruction": "<p>Bash your<strong> Fable pulled mushrooms</strong> with a <strong>rolling pin </strong>to break them up</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>bashed</strong> <strong>Fable pulled mushrooms </strong>with a generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and cook for 5-6 min or until browned, breaking them up with a wooden spoon as you go – these are your <strong>pulled Fable mushrooms</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1682590033336-x200.jpg",
