            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the mushrooms are cooking, zest <strong>half</strong> your<strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>lime[s]</strong> (try to grate lightly with a micro-plane or sharp box grater and avoid grating the white pith, as this is very bitter)</p><p>Chop the<strong> lime[s]</strong> in half</p><p>Crush your <strong>roasted peanuts</strong> with a <strong>rolling pin</strong></p><p>Tip: If you don’t have a rolling pin, just chop them roughly!</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1682590036747-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
