            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>finely chopped chilli </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) to a bowl with the juice of the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>lime[s]</strong>, <strong>half</strong> your <strong>soy sauce</strong>, <strong>half</strong> the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>garlic </strong>(you'll use the rest later!), 3 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[4 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[6 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong> and 3 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[4 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[6 tbsp]<strong> </span>cold water</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>Vietnamese-style dressing</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1682590039602-x200.jpg",
