            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the<strong> </strong>pulled Fable<strong> </strong>mushrooms have browned, add the <strong>remaining soy sauce</strong>,<strong> remaining chopped</strong> <strong>garlic</strong> and <strong>lime zest</strong> to the pan</p><p>Stir it all together and cook for a final 1 min or until fragrant – these are your <strong>Vietnamese-style pulled Fable mushrooms</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
